    compset="Sorcery"
    isunique="yes"
    description="{b}Blood Mark:{/b} the ability to mark an object with your own blood. A mage can feel the object's presence when it is nearby or know where it might be at a distance.{br}{br}{b}Pull:{/b} the ability to open a portal to pull a Marked object to you.{br}{br}{b}Walk:{/b} This allows the sorcier to open a portal and walk to a location or object he has Marked."
