  <thing
    id="soMatushki"
    name="Dar Matushki"
    compset="Sorcery"
    isunique="yes"
    description="{b}'Mother's Touch'{/b}{br}{br}Matushka sought you out because she wanted to teach you a Lesson. Each lesson includes supernatural Gifts and Restrictions.{br}{br}{b}Gift: {/b}Your Lesson includes a supernatural power. You can use your power by spending a Hero Point.{br}{br}{b}Restriction: {/b}This is a limit on your behavior. So long as you maintain your Restriction, you can use the Lesson's Gift. Your Restriction also includes the price you must pay if you break the Restriction."
    summary="Ussaran Sorcery">
