    name="Hexenwork"
    compset="Sorcery"
    isunique="yes"
    description="Hexenwerk is a Sorcery practiced almost exclusively in Eisen. In many parts of the country, the Sorcery is illegal, punishable by death. In others, it is seen as a necessary tool to fight the horrors of the night. A {i}hexe{/i} is one who practices this forbidden art. Some use it to fight the undead of Eisen and others use it for more nefarious ends."
    summary="Eisen Sorcery">
    <fieldval field="sMinName" value="Minor Unguent"/>
    <fieldval field="sMajName" value="Major Unguent"/>
